lead_paragraph: BERNE, Switzerland, Nov. 23 -- Apparently indifferent to the possible reactions of an as yet uninformed public in France, the runaway collaborationist cabinet in Vichy continued today its final preparations to bring France economically, politically and militarily into the Axis orbit.
abstract: Berne sources see Vichy Cabinet making final moves to bring France into Axis orbit
